Package org.ipdr.api

Contains IPDR collector API classes

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
ConnectInfo The interface represents a Connect message information.
ConnectionController The interface allows to control the ability of establishing flow start state in a connection
ConnectionControllerFactory This interface relates to a connection controller factory
DisconnectInfo The interface represents a DISCONNECT message information.
FlowStartInfo The interface represents a FLOW_START message information.
FlowStopInfo The interface represents a FLOW_STOP message information.
Outputter An interface for encapsulating the methods for outputting values for a record from the Collector.
OutputterFactory  
ProbingListener The interface is used for probing sessions of a specified exporter
SessionStartInfo The interface represents a SESSION_START message information.
SessionStopInfo The interface represents a SESSION_STOP message information.
StateMachineListener The interface provides a convenient way to peek into protocol state machine
TemplateNegotiator Provides interface for custom template negotiators
TemplateNegotiatorFactory An interface to create instances of TemplateNegotiator
 

Class Summary
CollectorManager The class provides access to IPDR protocol.
ConnectionThread The class represents a single connection thread
 

Exception Summary
ConnectionIOException Exception thrown when an I/O error happens during reading or writing on the TCP connection.
OutputterException Exception thrown when there's an error in outputting data.
 

Package org.ipdr.api Description

Contains IPDR collector API classes
